{"tid":466853,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人試過黃秋生煮法出前一丁???","createTime":"2017-11-13T03:16:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-16T19:12:03.000Z","uid":11512,"like":11,"dislike":168,"uniUserReply":107,"replies":[{"pid":"b9802dc5a8e4e125bb38c5f4962bbba14260dfe4","tid":466853,"uid":11512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T03:16:43.000Z","msg":"平時自己煮開既方法:-<br />\n<br />\n1. 煲滾水<br />\n2. 落出前一丁<br />\n3. 啲面開始散果陣熄火<br />\n4. 過冷河再將面放落碗到<br />\n5. 煲過煲新既滾水<br />\n6. 落味粉落碗再落滾水<br />\n7. 食得<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n之前睇過黃秋生既煮法係:-<br />\n<br />\n1. 拎個煲裝水&lt;---未洗開火煲住<br />\n2. 放出前一丁落個煲到<br />\n3. 開火<br />\n4. 啲水同面岩岩滾果陣就落味粉<br />\n5. 滾晒就熄火<br />\n6. 食得<br />\n<br />\n佢話自己果套先係最傳統既煮法，各位點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"265ffe3c77ef6ad1faa1af87c207f8e4122c9327","tid":466853,"uid":65984,"like":38,"dislike":1,"score":37,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T03:22:09.000Z","msg":"要講埋重點, 一定要係日版丁"},{"pid":"39d384218f036abbc7bed99169d86d70e38c39b2","tid":466853,"uid":2419,"like":313,"dislike":12,"score":301,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T03:23:43.000Z","msg":"食公仔麵都要過冷河<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15197caa4b4913ec1165edb5fdf32228a31efa31","tid":466853,"uid":29128,"like":120,"dislike":5,"score":115,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T03:26:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>食公仔麵都要過冷河<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢樣真 浪費時間<br />\n麵又淡"},{"pid":"f7057d3fb4b98613e115d9068f4380206d62c200","tid":466853,"uid":11512,"like":10,"dislike":188,"score":-178,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T03:28:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>食公仔麵都要過冷河<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢樣真 浪費時間<br />\n麵又淡</blockquote><br />\n生活態度黎"},{"pid":"4bb9c84ced561aa06eca0f95db3c77028b2de645","tid":466853,"uid":11512,"like":3,"dislike":9,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T03:30:29.000Z","msg":