uid":19908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T04:16:36.000Z","msg":"開滾水浸個麵落去 再拎去微波爐叮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9d0afc9c87817c11f10dde4458d9ecee7147b10","tid":466853,"uid":76527,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T04:19:00.000Z","msg":"冷水個下落面，你煮得散都過左3分鐘啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81647850cd686b9d18179f79211d82786ef8d8c7","tid":466853,"uid":3896,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T04:20:20.000Z","msg":"但水未滾就落麵, 唔會浸到淋咩<br />\n但水滾先落麵, d麵一有少少散開就撈起<br />\n次次都好彈牙喎<br />\n<br />\n利申 同樓主煮法 除咗冷河<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f2045e59fa7699562bf3aadbf44399e6f4033b6","tid":466853,"uid":22387,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T04:22:45.000Z","msg":"冷水+麵+粉<br />\n微波爐叮5分鍾<br />\n落麻油 食得"},{"pid":"9ad4d46513e712136da585defd488196f57a93c3","tid":466853,"uid":188,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T04:23:40.000Z","msg":"鬼唔撚知過冷河 分開水味精湯好食少少咩<br />\n黃你老母秋生煮法"},{"pid":"354ae75dba56214185025734dbc1ec65cd7e7d6d","tid":466853,"uid":28469,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T04:23:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>黃秋生果個真係幾好用<br />\n滾個下通常都係硬身嘅麵（本人唔鐘意食淋麵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n電視睇到之後用到而家</blockquote><br />\n認同 快靚正"},{"pid":"60e24d05d3eaddeb11d6c2c8f8d1f5c98f1a834a","tid":466853,"uid":83016,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T04:24:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有冇人係直接用個煲黎食<br />\n水滾落麵 成煲攞起就咁食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bcef3873d0a18642afb88e3b6e55aa909ad2429","tid":466853,"uid":20454,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T04:25:12.000Z","msg":"一次過煲兩份水<br />\n水滾舀起湯底份量落碗(已落粉)開左個湯佢<br />\n落麵煮<br />\n煮完夾起d麵放落碗湯度<br />\n落麻油/另加辣油(只食麻油味)<br />\n倒煮麵水，開水喉水浸煲<br />\n拎碗麵返房食<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9296b811b0b8eae48e18310c7dcfa409dca24465","tid":466853,"uid":142532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T04:26:10.000Z","msg":"個麵仲要係深色果面向下咁落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c325f7c3e60cca37138b74fc90e6e43f9126501","tid":466853,"uid":42178,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T04:27:08.000Z","msg":"佢個方法有樣好,唔洗等水滾"},{"pid":"18a41b7e7b1682f6b81e0199a5229052bc248c32","tid":466853,"uid":29040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T04:27:13.000Z","msg":"過冷河先淋喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過屋企版一丁麵質係好淋 點煮都係<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n要好食一定要用餐廳版一丁再用黃秋生煮法，煮個陣千祈唔好揚散個面"},{"pid":"c19d2956a6b051839781d4b1c210e49c015f9020","tid":466853,"uid":1629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T04:27:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有冇人係直接用個煲黎食<br />\n水滾落麵 成煲攞起就咁食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n識食..水滾乜柒都放晒落去, 最後放面等個面一散就關火成煲拎出廳食..<br />\n利申: 唔會飲湯"},{"pid":"12a9798d22857d9861cf177e3fdc365fc68ea4b5","tid":466853,"uid":42178,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T04:27:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個麵仲要係深色果面向下咁落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我習慣淺色果面向下"},{"pid":"cf2be0852068a670385b3adc17f1fd1ed67f1020","tid":466853,"uid":4349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T04:27:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>食公仔麵都要過冷河<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我以為過冷河係熟咗過一過凍水再放返份熱湯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係熟左過凍水 等佢爽口啲無咁&quot;林&quot;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔過冷河既話硬係覺得比平時&quot;林&quot;啲麵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n哂撚氣<br />\n公仔麵過完冷河 落番熱湯到，唔夠1分鐘又林哂<br />\n公仔麵既特性就係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49982beaeebaa858d214be450840bec42602337b","tid":466853,"uid":20438,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T04:27:54.000Z","msg":"我老母用生秋王個方法<br />\n<br />\n我就<br />\n煲滾水<br />\n落面煮3分鐘左右<br />\n室溫水用碗開粉<br />\n直接夾面落碗<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n又快又做到過冷河"},{"pid":"f1c4bc65058df7f605b6202f797680ad93415eea","tid":466853,"uid":24696,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T04:28:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冷水+麵+粉<br />\n微波爐叮5分鍾<br />\n落麻油 食得</blockquote><br />\n同你一樣會叮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n叮完真係會彈d"},{"pid":"bff83b8503c5fa0389c01c72fe424e07792c8bbc","tid":466853,"uid":111253,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T04:29:48.000Z","msg":"蒸兩塊午餐肉, 一隻蛋(半生熟) <br />\n隔離同時煲定滾水<br />\n餐肉+蛋倒落空碗到, 督穿蛋黃<br />\n放麵落滾水, 麵散就錨起放落碗到,<br />\n倒滾水落碗, 少許鹽同雞粉, 搞掂"},{"pid":"879f80c0b3e2b45e36357c321e16c54dd0b4648d","tid":466853,"uid":84355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T04:30:27.000Z","msg":"唔洗煲過煲新水煮湯底架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df5051f771e2c1f09e0123635dd5e4d4bf31f57a","tid":466853,"uid":4349,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T04:33:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>個麵仲要係深色果面向下咁落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我習慣淺色果面向下</blockquote><br />\n咪錯囉 仲講出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n深色面係油底，比較硬<br />\n你淺色面放下煮，煮散哂d麵既時候，其實已經係太林"},{"pid":"4ab329c5d674cad6f65edd2197b7c5cefa615125","tid":466853,"uid":42178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T04:37:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>個麵仲要係深色果面向下咁落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我習慣淺色果面向下</blockquote><br />\n咪錯囉 仲講出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n深色面係油底，比較硬<br />\n你淺色面放下煮，煮散哂d麵既時候，其實已經係太林</blockquote><br />\n細個煮麵果陣因為深色果邊比較似煮完隻色,同埋淺色果邊摸落乾d<br />\n所以大個左都下意識咁做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94d47ea886a586dec253957cb496fc92231a2b61","tid":466853,"uid":29080,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T04:37:40.000Z","msg":"戇鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81cd5be3ba5c9854b515bcebd63b81415c2dbe2a","tid":466853,"uid":5315,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T04:39:02.000Z","msg":"屌你老母搞咁撚多野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e81e77b9b1b1fc40c1033dc2d0acdbac270a2f3b","tid":466853,"uid":14244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T04:39:34.000Z","msg":"煮個公仔麵姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e98bbb337a566ac0f4612f48d399fcd68579aac","tid":466853,"uid":120892,"like":0,"dislike":11,"score":-11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T04:40:40.000Z","msg":"我中意食啲麵爽口彈牙，不過煮法就真係睇有冇時間<br />\n<br />\n有時間嘅話：<br />\n1  煲水，水滾落麵落半包粉<br />\n2  揚散d麵馬上關火倒曬d水，麵擺埋一邊<br />\n3  煮過煲新嘅水，今次落曬剩餘嘅粉同落配菜（肥牛、叉燒、芝士魚蛋之類）<br />\n4  夾曬所有配菜上個麵度，攞舊芝士刨上個麵上面（唔好用卡夫果d）<br />\n5  將湯倒落去個面上面，融咗啲芝士<br />\n6  撈一撈已經食得<br />\n<br />\n咁做嘅好處同原因：<br />\n1.  第一煲水用半包粉令麵帶少少味，煮得果幾分鐘本來就難令麵入味啦<br />\n2.  即食麵始終落咗好多化學嘢，第一煲水過一過都係想少d化學嘢，幫助不大但好過冇咁<br />\n3.  味道方面，第二煲水個湯加配菜其實夠味，尤其如果你煲到得番半碗水嘅話，味道已經夠曬<br />\n4.  用湯嘅熱力融咗d芝士，點冇味嘅都有配菜同芝士味搭救啦<br />\n<br />\n冇時間嘅話：<br />\n仲咁講究咩，乜都隊曬落去，水滾馬上落麵，揚散佢關火倒水食啦"},{"pid":"48b6d971329f4a26c0902337571219f52323a8c6","tid":466853,"uid":47202,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T04:46:32.000Z","msg":"煲水, 開面倒粉落碗, 水滾, 倒一碗滾水落碗, 淨番滾水落面, 落面煮開, 筲箕隔水, 放落碗湯, 落麻油. 食得....<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n主要想減少食個面既棕櫚油<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce0b5666703544fdaf9cdc2f0ee8f04d05ed25e2","tid":466853,"uid":7632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T04:50:12.000Z","msg":"1）滾水落麵<br />\n2）水過麵身<br />\n3）千祈唔好攪麵<br />\n4）一般少過兩分鐘<br />\n5）保持麵餅形狀上碗<br />\n6）落味精<br />\n7）大滾水落碗至麵完全浸泡<br />\n8）吱麻油於匙羹中，盛滿味精湯，之後一口喝下！<br />\n9）麵浸於味精湯中半分鐘<br />\n10）食得！"},{"pid":"d462787fc215cc52284e673be847d48ff08fbaaa","tid":466853,"uid":13421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T04:54:11.000Z","msg":"樓主真係戇鳩仔"},{"pid":"7d8ea79f28afcc32346d44cb11ba3e60bb4dc250","tid":466853,"uid":4349,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T04:56:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>煲水, 開面倒粉落碗, 水滾, 倒一碗滾水落碗, 淨番滾水落面, 落面煮開, 筲箕隔水, 放落碗湯, 落麻油. 食得....<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n主要想減少食個面既棕櫚油<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nSame<br />\n咁最正路"},{"pid":"0272c925392aab0e919dda3c48227f0c4a6cccda","tid":466853,"uid":4349,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T04:57:53.000Z","msg":"不過如果煮辛辣麵 係完全路同煮法<br />\n一定要落粉煲水，再落麵一齊煮<br />\n咁先係最入味"},{"pid":"f5e4d02b6a07e6c87fca1a3ac0655cbf85e08104","tid":466853,"uid":4349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T04:58:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>不過如果煮辛辣麵 係完全唔同煮法<br />\n一定要落粉煲水，再落麵一齊煮<br />\n咁先係最入味</blockquote>"},{"pid":"2b9fa4f5afa71d69ba2cf8a98cfbbef1f151034e","tid":466853,"uid":11320,"like":9,"dislike":3,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T05:01:29.000Z","msg":"上面成班以為自己好叻食個麵好快好有效率<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 人地問點煮好食，成班爭住講最緊要快，驚死人地唔知自己係港奴咁"},{"pid":"d37be81f2308170a434cbc449b2628ae998c2c61","tid":466853,"uid":43493,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T05:03:40.000Z","msg":"1. 水滾落麵，煮三分鐘<br />\n2. 味粉落碗<br />\n3. 煮好麵撈起，fing走多餘水分，放落有味粉個碗<br />\n4. 撈均味粉同麵<br />\n5. 倒煲麵水落去，加麻油"},{"pid":"461703e131592afdc5d7c79908b5557d2180b696","tid":466853,"uid":150796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T05:11:17.000Z","msg":"細個10歲前淨係識煮公仔面個時<br />\n阿爺教黃秋生煮法<br />\n<br />\n之後阿爺走左唔知幾時開始身邊啲人煮乜都滾水落<br />\n個時開始𨍭左做滾水落面"},{"pid":"de5eb52bc6041dc946bc41b48ac08a0f9d088ba1","tid":466853,"uid":11512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T05:11:36.000Z","msg":"討論下姐 唔洗咁激動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n趕時間既話更係拿拿林碌熟去就算啦<br />\n咁有時間既話都可以花小小時間心機整好食啲既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcb25d5904f6281aa6fe76440965f11bb3de4111","tid":466853,"uid":150796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T05:11:43.000Z","msg":"食唔出日版同港版有乜分別..."},{"pid":"85140b67b09d37c49d2c637b86e8f62529ba3759","tid":466853,"uid":28195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T05:12:03.000Z","msg":"秋生既煮法，夜深時間最快有得食"},{"pid":"60541faad624c4fc6606ce7c5cfb21c9c69b2d14","tid":466853,"uid":27324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T05:12:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>1. 水滾落麵，煮三分鐘<br />\n2. 味粉落碗<br />\n3. 煮好麵撈起，fing走多餘水分，放落有味粉個碗<br />\n4. 撈均味粉同麵<br />\n5. <span style=\"color: red;\">倒煲麵水</span>落去，加麻油</blockquote><br />\n用煲麵水已經唔掂啦 梗係用新既滾水黎食麵"},{"pid":"04e4c1b7554895d084fdd18b7373da8b82845b9f","tid":466853,"uid":28195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T05:12:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>食唔出日版同港版有乜分別...</blockquote><br />\n唔係掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\